window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ryan is free... or is he?</b></p> <p>Incursions through the Divided Realms continue to pick up. Ryan seems to have escaped from those who summoned him, but could it be that they're just letting him out on a longer leash? Even if he can escape them, he can't escape the monsters who are spreading through the realms.</p> <p>Worse, his shadow is filled with all types of spidery things, and doesn't want to let him out of her sight. Crazy can be good right?</p>"; 
